  "prompt": "Why was Divya Bharti's death so controversial?",
  "response": "Divya Bharti's untimely death on April 5, 1993, remains one of Bollywood's most tragic and controversial events. Several factors contributed to the enduring controversy surrounding her passing:\n\n1. **Circumstances of Her Death**:\n   - **Accidental Overdose**: The official cause of death was reported as an accidental overdose of alcohol and sleeping pills. Bharti was found dead in her Mumbai apartment at the young age of 19, just as her career was skyrocketing.\n   - **Suspected Foul Play**: Despite the official findings, many fans and industry insiders found the circumstances suspicious. There were rumors of foul play, although no concrete evidence was ever presented to substantiate these claims.\n\n2. **Inconsistent Autopsy Reports**:\n   - There were inconsistencies and delays in the autopsy and investigation process. Such discrepancies fueled speculations about whether the investigation had been thorough and impartial.\n\n3. **Rumors and Speculations**:\n   - **Romantic Entanglements**: Bharti's relationships, both personal and professional, were often the subject of media scrutiny. Speculations about jealous rivals or disgruntled associates added to the mystery.\n   - **Threatening Letters**: Reports emerged that",
